metadata.name: Cyanide & Happiness Unrevealed
metadata.description: The Cyanide & Happiness NFT by explosm uses stick figure art to present graphic, dark and often surreal humor which has been described as seeming to have no taste boundaries whatsoever, covering topics such as abortion, suicide, violence, and necrophilia. Owning NFT grants you rights to the specific comic and a permanent patreon benefits.
